SHIPPING INTEGRATION

Shipping Gateways:

1. USPS - Distance.
2. FedEx - Requires weight and dimensions.
3. UPS- Requires weight and dimensions.

Note: Shipping gateways will not work if requirements is not set.

Steps in Shipping Integration.
1. Upload and Activate Plugin.
2. Go to WooCommerce > Settings > Shipping
3. Click 'USPS Basic' > Enable.
4. Input Credentials provided by the Client.
5. Check Services.
6. Click save changes.
